## 9. Architecture

```
[Knowledge Base Docs]
      │
      ▼
[Chunker + Embedder] ──► [Vector Store (in-memory/FAISS)]
                                   │
[Golden Dataset (questions)]      │
      │                           │
      ▼                           ▼
[Eval Runner] ──query──► [Retriever] ──chunks──► [Generator (LLM API)]
      │                                                  │
      │◄──────────────── response, timing, tokens ───────┘
      ▼
[Scorer] ── context precision/recall / faithfulness / answer relevancy / latency / cost
      │
      ▼
[Results Store] (SQLite, append-only, run_id indexed)
      │
      ▼
[Regression Checker] ── compares vs baseline (config.yaml thresholds)
      │
      ▼
[Slack Alerter] (fires only on threshold breach)
```

Triggered by: GitHub Actions on every push to `main` + nightly cron (catches silent provider-side model drift with zero code change on your end).

