## 10. Tech Stack

- **Language:** Python
- **Embeddings:** `sentence-transformers` (local, free, no API cost for the SUT's retrieval step)
- **Vector search:** plain numpy cosine similarity to start (20 docs doesn't need FAISS) — swap to FAISS later if you want the line on your resume
- **LLM Access:** Anthropic/OpenAI SDK for the generation step
- **Storage:** SQLite (simple, queryable, no infra)
- **CI:** GitHub Actions (`.github/workflows/eval.yml`)
- **Alerting:** Slack Incoming Webhook (`requests.post`)
- **Reporting:** Markdown/HTML report per run, uploaded as a GitHub Actions artifact

